</div>
<div>
<p>　　<persName>丁大全</persName>字<name key="丁大全" type="zi">子<num value="10000">萬</num>
</name>
<pc>，</pc>鎮江人<pc>。</pc>面藍色<pc>。</pc>嘉熙<measure quantity="2" unit="years">
<num value="2">二</num>年</measure>舉<term>進士</term>
<pc>，</pc>調蕭山尉<pc>。</pc>上謁帥閫<pc>，</pc>
